snippet.title: Pikmin Stellar: Shop Trailer
snippet.description:
Louie and Davey discuss what Louie plans on doing with the money he's collecting in the 404 solar system.

Bobu's Bargains is a wonderland of all the merchandise a space captain could ever need! I'm sure all your Pokos are going to a good cause...

Check out more Pikmin Stellar updates on the official discord server!
https://discord.gg/NUWksAjFwz
